                text = "*(A child sits apart from the others — every era has its grave-eyed serious child — with a scrap of parchment, or a wax tablet, or a strip of bark, and a stub of something to write with, carefully printing names in a careful, laborious hand. They look up at you with the grave directness of a child engaged in important work, and decide, after a quick appraisal, that you can be trusted.)* I'm making a list. *(matter-of-fact.)* Don't worry, you're not on it. It's not *that* kind of list. *(they pat the space beside them.)* It's a list of people nobody else is going to remember. I do one a day, at least. Sometimes more, if it's been a bad day for it. *(they squint at you.)* Do you know anybody nobody's going to remember? You can tell me their name. I'll add them. I'm very careful with the spelling.",
